data.description: Such a beautiful piece of property! This home is nestled on a little over 7 1/2 acres in the Red Level community. The home is only 16 minutes from Andalusia which has Walmart and all the grocery stores you can imagine! This property offers a 20x30 barn shed and 40x50 pole barn. There is a large fenced in portion that can be used for livestock (Appx 6 acres). This home offers original hardwood floors all throughout. With a little over 2300 heated and cool living space and around 1600 attic space that is floored and could easily be turned into an additional heated and cool area with a bedroom and/or office/bonus room. The primary bedroom has recently been added with a beautiful rustic feel to it with a laundry room and bathroom. The outdoor living area offers a custom bar and cooking area with plenty of seating and room to entertain. Schedule your tour today! This home has so much to offer!
